  <ability>
    <abilitytitle>Fine Art</abilitytitle>
    <abilityid>arts.fine_art</abilityid>
    <abilityactiontype><non-combat/></abilityactiontype>
    <tags><arts/></tags>
    <abilitydescription>
      <p>
  	The character has some ability, experience and training in painting, sculpting,
  	art history and appraisal.  They have worked for a master craftsman for
  	a number of years.  They know of, and can recognize, the great masters and
  	can provide information about the provenence of works of art.
      </p>
      <p>
  	At third level The character can create good works of art, and can make a good
  	living creating	art, if they choose to do so.  They may have rich and powerful
  	patrons that will provide some support in times of need.  Given a few weeks,
  	access to the art-work and the necessary equipment they are able to craft
  	forgeries that are hard to detect.
      </p>
    </abilitydescription>
    <spline><p x="30" y="30"/></spline>
    <prereqabilitylevel>arts.lore_1</prereqabilitylevel>
    <abilitycheck dc="12"/>
    <abilitychecktype>Std+Level</abilitychecktype>
    <abilitydmg></abilitydmg>
    <abilitylevels from="1" to="6"/>
  </ability>


